; Simple equilateral triangle, 100 mm sides
; With scale=0.001 in gcode.cfg this draws a 10 cm triangle.
; Gcode (0,0) = bottom-left corner of the triangle.
;
;         (50, 87)
;           /\
;          /  \
;         /    \
;  (0,0) /______\ (100,0)
;
; Z > 0  → travel (arm lifted)
; Z < 0  → draw  (force/admittance mode, marker presses paper)
;
; Note: pen transitions to draw mode WHILE moving from (0,0) to (100,0),
; so there is no stationary poke at the origin.

G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; travel above bottom-left, lifted
G01 X100 Y0 Z-1     ; press + move to bottom-right  (starts drawing mid-stroke)
G01 X50 Y87         ; right edge   →  apex
G01 X0 Y0           ; left edge    →  back to start
G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; lift off
